	<blockquote>“The Hidden” is what they call us.  A band of strong warriors and magical casters have 
	formed an alliance of strong friendship and firm leadership.  We are The Hidden, for people 
	see us infrequently, if ever at all.  And yet the public hears much of our doings, and 
	tells stories of our mysterious encounters.  Rumors are passed in the Seafarer's Roost, 
	parents of the high tree-top city, Kelethin, tell bedtime stories to their children; all 
	questioning who takes part in the small group of warriors, and where they could be right 
	now. What could they be doing right now?  In reality, no one knows.  Yet that is the way of 
	us, the small group of adventures out to bring Adventure, Life and Death, Love and Hate, 
	and Humor and Grief to Norrath.  We are, as they call us, The Hidden.</blockquote>

